dc_description_s: This data represents Public Land Survey System (PLSS) corners for Dodge County, Wisconsin in 2025. [The E8 database contains a collection of all uniquely identifiable local-level PLSS data available in digital format, and aggregates that data into a standardized schema and format. It also includes section, quarter-section, and quarter-quarter-section level polygons. The construction of the PLSS corner locations contained within the database relies on the local level coordinate information. This unique aspect of the database, allows for an accurate representation of the on-the-ground location of the PLSS corners.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
